Hi,

I don't know who build the original cs1.6 map.
My clan members requested i convert it to source.
Layout is as it was in 1.6, i just added some source props and a 3d skybox.

It's a mini map but who ever made it has devised some clever routing. I find it very playable and hope you like it as well.

More info on my site on building etc
